'''''Onslaught''''' is a video game that was released by [[Hewson Consultants|Hewson]] in 1989 for the [[Amiga]] and subsequently [[porting|ported]] to the [[Atari ST]], [[MS-DOS]], and [[Mega Drive]]. The game is a fantasy-themed [[platform game]] with an eerie soundtrack and graphic violence.

''Onslaught'' was re-released for [[iOS]] in December 2008 and for the [[Xbox 360]] in January 2009 for the [[Xbox 360]] via [[Xbox Live]].

==Plot==
